    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important; 
            ">Jet-helicopter crash update</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-jan-31-1.png" alt="Jet-helicopter crash update" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4"><strong>Summary: The investigation of the incident is underway, recovery operations were suspended during the night, and Trump blames Democrats for the incident.</strong></p>

          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">After the deadly crash of the regional passenger airline American Airlines Flight 5342 and a military black hawk, all 64 members aboard the flight were feared to be dead. The fire chief said that they are switching from a rescue operation to a recovery operation. The body of the plane was found upside-down in three sections in waist-deep water. Recovery efforts have been suspended until Friday morning (<a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-31-01-2025-h1-1-follow-live-updates?source=website" target="_blank">follow live updates</a>).</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4;filter:blur(5px);"><a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-31-01-2025-h1-2-the-natca?source=website" target="_blank">The NATCA</a> said it's premature to speculate on the cause of the incident. Investigators have recovered black boxes from the plane and will submit the preliminary report in 30 days. <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ ps-31-01-2025-h1-3-american-airlines-ceo?source=website"  target="_blank">American Airlines CEO</a> confirmed that the pilots aboard were not newcomers to commercial flights. At the time of the collision, one air traffic controller was working <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-31-01-2025-h1-4-two-different-tower-positions?source=website" target="_blank">two different tower positions</a> and handling both jet and helicopter traffic, which is believed to be a common practice.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column> 
    </mj-section>
